Based on a list of "rules" I've used for years to improve my finances and become a better person. The affirmations are either my own creation or my own spin on classics. My spouse encouraged me to create this collection because mental health matters. They also designed the affirmations. We collaborated on this and it was really fun.

There will be fifteen (15) affirmations in this collection.

The breakdown is as follows:
1. 10 Common affirmations x100M
2. 3 Rare affirmations x10M
3. 1 Super rare affirmation x210,000
4. 1 Legendary affirmation x1 (This affirmation is part of the collection but not for sale)

Thank you for your support and for spreading our affirmations. We hope they help you and make you feel good.

*No website, no Discord, no Twitter. Just good vibes & positive energy.*

The history of Istanbul can be divided into five major periods: Prehistoric period,Byzantionperiod,Eastern Romanperiod,Ottomanperiod, and Turkey period.

 Istanbul is a city that has been among the most important and largest metropolises of the world for about sixteen centuries, from the 4th century to the 20th century.  It has been the undisputed sole ruler of a wide region where the continents of Europe, Asia and Africa meet, and has managed to significantly affect world history in this process.

 Istanbul for one thousand six hundred years, from 330 to 1922;  It is a city that served as the capital of 4 different empires: Roman Empire (330-395), Byzantine Empire (395-1204, 1261-1453), Latin Empire (1204-1261) and Ottoman Empire (1453-1922).  Three of these empires went down in history as the most powerful and powerful states in the world during their existence.
